http2.command: node --max-old-space-size=65536 http2 url 120 10 10 live.txt --redirect true --ratelimit true --query true

http1.command: node --max-old-space-size=65536 http1 POST url live.txt 120 10 10 cookie= randomstring= headerdata= postdata=

httpmix.command: node --max-old-space-size=65536 httpmix POST "url" 120 10 128 live.txt --query 1 --delay 1 --cookie "bypassing=%RAND%" --referer rand --http mix --close --randpath --parsed --reset --multipath 5 --header "User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0#Accept: */*" --ua "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64)" --header "Authorization: Bearer token123#X-Custom-Header: value123"

get.command: node --max-old-space-size=65536 get GET "url" 120 10 128 live.txt --query 1 --delay 10 --cookie "bypassing=%RAND%" --referer rand --http mix --close --randpath --parsed --reset --multipath "path1@path2@path3@path4@path5" --header "User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0#Accept: */*" --ua "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64)" --header "Authorization: Bearer token123#X-Custom-Header: value123"
